      "content": "hey, i'm starting this new blog about global lifestyle and stuff. i want to make a \"universal guide to professional etiquette and sophistication\" that people can use anywhere in the world for business or high-end social events. can u give me an outline of the main sections i should include to make sure someone looks truly sophisticated and professional no matter where they are? thanks!",
